<h4 id="참고-mac에서-ec2-접속-방법">참고. mac에서 EC2 접속 방법</h4>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">ssh <span class="nt">-i</span> <span class="o">[</span>AWS Key pem file path] ec2-user@[EC2 HOST URL]</code></pre></figure>

